description: Crunch into taco night with this quick and easy dinner recipe. Using a hard shell taco kit, you'll have tasty beef tacos seasoned to perfection in no time.
keywords: Taco,Seafood free,Tree nut free,Egg free,Low sugar,Sesame free,Beef,Fakeaway,Soy free,Mince,Peanut free
name: Beef Tacos Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 1 corn cob, husks and silks removed

recipeInstructions.text: Cut kernels from corn cob. Heat a large frying pan over high heat. Cook corn, stirring, for 5 minutes or until charred. Transfer to a bowl.

Heat oil in same frying pan over high heat. Add mince and cook, breaking up lumps with a wooden spoon, for 8 minutes or until well browned. Add taco seasoning from kit and cook, stirring, for 1 minute or until fragrant.
Meanwhile, heat taco shells from kit according to packet instructions.
Fill taco shells with beef mixture, corn, sour cream, salsa from kit and coriander. Serve with lime.
